## ─── Get Recipes ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name GetRecipes
GET {{baseurl}}/recipes?page=1&per_page=10
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Token: admin:admin123

###


## ─── Delete Recipe ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name DeleteRecipe
DELETE {{baseurl}}/recipes/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Token: admin:admin123

###
